  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this Post Market Surveillance Validation is to document the performance and
      clinical outcomes of the Polaris Deformity Spinal System &amp; Trivium 3D Spinal Deformity
      Correction System.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this Post Market Surveillance Validation is to document the performance and
      clinical outcomes of the Polaris Deformity Spinal System &amp; Trivium 3D Spinal Deformity
      Correction System. We have extended the study tol collect further outcomes data at the 12
      month time point.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
